7 Section 4. The Make America Healthy Again Kentucky Task Force shall at a
8 minimum meet monthly during the 2025 Interim of the General Assembly and shall
9 submit recommendations to the Governor and to the Legislative Research Commission
10 for referral to the Interim Joint Committee on Health Services by December 1, 2025.
11 Section 5. Provisions of this section to the contrary notwithstanding, the
12 Legislative Research Commission shall have the authority to alternatively assign the
13 issues identified herein to an interim joint committee or subcommittee thereof, and to
14 designate a study completion date.
15 Section 6. The Clerk of the Senate is directed to transmit a copy of this
16 Resolution to the Governor, each member of Kentucky’s Congressional delegation, and
17 the secretary of Cabinet for Health and Family Services, the Commissioner of the
18 Kentucky Department of Agriculture, and the commissioner of the Kentucky Department
19 of Education, for review and consideration in advancing the goals of the Make America
20 Healthy Again movement to make Kentucky healthy again.
